description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 6.1 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Computers that are effective as of June 2, 2014. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=computers.pr_crit_computers
